  "text": "As previous research has observed, there is no coherent notion of the audience an individual thinks is communicating with online [CITATION_1] , leading to a variety of behaviours based on the individual perceptions of the viewer. These issues form part of a much greater problem concerning abusive behaviour online that defies any straightforward design solution, requiring further research on behavioural norms online.",
